cs.SE, cs.PL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY. 

The paper discusses a technique for automated program repair, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The technique involves syntactic program transformations (cs.PL) and explores fix candidates exhaustively up to a provided bound (cs.AI). The paper also presents a novel mechanism to detect and prune infeasible fix candidates (cs.SY). Finally, the evaluation is performed on a benchmark of faulty Java container classes (cs.PL).
